  "title": "Sales Admin",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities :</strong></p><p>1. Preparation of project documentations (Site Clearance, Name List, PTW, Risk Assessment etc)</p><p>2. Assist in planning for jobs required according to work schedule and requirements and ensure budget and cost are in control.</p><p>3. Coordinate with customers and plan for job schedules. Evaluate customer needs and respond effectively with a good plan.</p><p>4. Liaise with operations and sales team on customers’ feedbacks and complaints</p><p>5. Liaise with operations and sales team and accounts department for timely billing of work done</p><p>6. Maintaining proper department filings and records</p><p>7. Assist in preparations of quotations, and internal registration.</p><p>8. Renewal and maintain relevant licenses.</p><p>9. Provide administration support to the Operations/ Sales Team</p><p>10. Assume any other duties suitable duties as and when assigned by the Company</p><p><strong>Requirements :</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least a \"O\"/\"N\" Level, Diploma, Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma, Bachelor's Degree, Post Graduate Diploma, Professional Degree, any field.</li><li>At least 2 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li><li>Full-Time position(s) available.</li></ul>",
